                  , Esq; at the same time and place, and taking from his person one gold watch, value 10 l. a steel chain, two steel seals, and 16 s. in monies numbered, his property. Also for assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t17820911-5-victim94" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Rainstead
