                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am servant to Mr. Alderman Kitchen, as coachman, Davis is the man that took the purse from Mr. Allen, I think the other is the man that had Mr. Allen's watch to the best of my knowledge.</p>
               <p>
            
